have a grid
    with obstacle

each deck is made of card specific to the caracter,
  archer deck
  knight deck
  space marine deck...
  
  and have a starter card

each round, player put a card on the grid, each card tell where the next card can be.


card:
    -relative tile attack
    -relative tile defense
    -relative tile movement
    -immediate effect
    
it is cards against cards
every turn you place a card in a tile that last placed card allow out.
every card change battle map behavior, bonus on attack,def, movement
every card allow you to move to certain tile
you only consider last card, as they are effective for only one turn
your card should attack last oponent card
